comment:
Hey L'Oreal, listen up!!!

I used to use a lot of L'Oreal products!  Every 6-8 weeks, I used Excellence Hair Coloring.  

I LOVED their hair dye as they always gave a tube of heavy duty conditioner to use after the dye is rinsed out.
I also LOVED their face care products, from face cleanser to moisturizer.  
And I LOVED their makeup.....

The common word being LOVED!!  I may still love & miss their products, but as long as this husband beating, lying, cheating, obnoxious, poor excuse for a woman, is their idea of a great "woman", they have LOST a customer!!

This is no " woman" it is a female, just as any man who hits a woman is no man, he is a male!!
She gets away with smuggling animals into another country & forging veterinary reports which should be jail time!  

I hope that when Johnny's case is heard in 2021, he wins everything he is asking for!!!  She abused him mentally & physically!  The absolute disgusting time was right after his mother died.  Only a heartless bitch would do what she did!

I was going to box all of the L'Oreal products up and ship them back to L'Oreal headquarters but they do not seem to have any offices in the USA, so I just threw them out!
While I realize L'Oreal won't miss me as a customer, but if everyone quit using their products, they might just get the message!!
I also will not waste a dime on tickets to Aquaman 2!  I will not buy the DVD or rent time on paying on demand!  
I noticed that Johnny was immediately removed as spokesperson for products and lost the next Pirates movie!!  No Captain Jack Sparrow, and they have a bland movie!!  Johnny is perfect and brought Captain Jack to life!!
I love how Johnny puts on the Captain Jack outfit and goes to the hospitals to visit sick children!  He remembers how he (& Vanessa!) felt when Lily-Rose almost lost her life!  Once they realized that Lily-Rose was going to live, he was able to look around at the other parents & especially at these sweet little children who suffer from painful conditions as well as painful tests & treatments!  
Those little ones don't smile much.  
But every video I have seen of "Captain Jack Sparrow" walking into those wards and all of those children had big smiles on their faces!!  
One of the most touching videos that I have seen is Johnny seeing a little girl behind the plastic curtains, unable to get a hug from him like the other children were able to do.  She was in the phase of the doctors destroying her immune system & not even her parents could be inside that room with her.
Her sweet little face watching as Johnny posed for photos & talked to each child!  But Johnny noticed her!  He went to the clear plastic curtain & put his hands up to her hands!  
Her family was able to get photos of her with Johnny, AKA Captain Jack Sparrow through the plastic curtain!  He sat on the floor as did she & spoke with him!   I hope she is in remission and is doing well!!

Thank goodness Lily-Rose made a complete recovery!  Johnny & Vanessa were still together back then.  They donated $2 million to the hospital which was in London!  

As for Amber, to quote Judge Judy, "Beauty fades, dumb is forever!!" 
Heard's beauty is fading fast!!  Very few actresses get continuous work after they turn 40.  Only the really good ones continue in front of the camera!  Heard is not a good actress, so she will be gone from the industry in about 10 years!

Imagine her at a drive-thru restaurant window!  She would throw your food & drinks in your face!

Johnny is so lucky that she didn't forget her birth control!  He would have to see her at the usual functions in a child's life!  And her, with a baby & that temper of hers??  That poor child would end up both mentally & physically by her!  
If she couldn't control her temper with a grown man, she would snap the first time that child makes her angry!!!
